seo: Apache Tika-server,命令执行漏洞,CVE-2018-1335,漏洞检测
summary: 该插件用于检测Apache Tika-server是否存在命令执行漏洞（CVE-2018-1335），通过发送特定HTTP请求验证目标是否受影响。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Apache Tika-server has a command execution vulnerability (CVE-2018-1335) by sending a specific HTTP request to verify if the target is affected.
